{"tid":1080710,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"走咗轉高登有感而發","createTime":"2019-03-27T19:23:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T19:36:04.000Z","uid":118886,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4ba9cd6474ae6cce3f04fed8fed75cd126e75e3e","tid":1080710,"uid":118886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T19:23:07.000Z","msg":"啱啱屎忽痕無野做諗住上舊登懷緬下以前啲舊post 本身都預咗嗰邊無乜人流 <br />\n點知係出乎意料 有改圖 改歌 畫圖 數量唔多但絕對係高質<br />\n再講討論風氣 雖然都係鳩up居多 不過我見到嘅唔係句句都copy式回覆 好似個個都無自己主見講黎講去都嗰幾樣野 以為自己好幽默話題離離去去都係女人係雞 再唔係就扮大袋笑下窮人 俾人話兒登真係唔怪得人"},{"pid":"be9b054d3d2d939c8b41d9571f45b0092bd72bf0","tid":1080710,"uid":204322,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T19:25:41.000Z","msg":"今日都睇過個張智霖同家燕媽媽改圖post 笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e394209880ca4365242133d5a1a6c0d59df66ba5","tid":1080710,"uid":118886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T19:32:29.000Z","msg":"透過 HKG 分享一則貼文：[高登音樂台]曲 / 高階擒拿手-千港豬 (原曲:初音未來-千本櫻)<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=7035208&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D7035208%26page%3D1&d=5mmA4sQKuQaI7%2FjJJ4WTl5gFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=e42a7154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=7035208&amp;page=1</a><br />\n<br />\n改歌方面真係好有心機 詞高質唔多講 個動畫真係無得輸 再睇翻佢地個YouTube channel真係每一首都好貼時事 連登我印象中今年都係得兩首係出到街<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n透過 HKG 分享一則貼文：[潛力圖]洩家燕痴LAM叫換証<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=7035104&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D7035104%26page%3D1&d=5mmA4sQKuQaI7%2FjJJ4WTl5gFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=a19fb005\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=7035104&amp;page=1</a><br />\n<br />\n再講下改圖 我認唔係全部有改嘅我都笑得出 但絕對係好笑同有創意嘅多 起碼我真係可以睇到大笑 連登依邊啲改圖我唔評論大家都知"},{"pid":"5950f2e074be0fefdf03b285a324e2458d70ee23","tid":1080710,"uid":118886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be9b054d3d2d939c8b41d9571f45b0092bd72bf0","tid":1080710,"uid":204322,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T19:25:41.000Z","msg":"今日都睇過個張智霖同家燕媽媽改圖post 笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T19:36:04.000Z","msg":"頭先睇嗰陣都好有以前追post嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}